{"tid":2497014,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩男生被控管有噴漆及易燃有機溶劑 分被判入勞教及更生中心","createTime":"2021-04-20T08:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T11:08:59.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c0bd49a8770e924784414d715f4ab21423885749","tid":2497014,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:18:53.000Z","msg":"兩名分別18及16歲的男學生於去年5月在旺角新世紀廣場分別管有噴漆、雷射筆、易燃有機溶劑等物品。18歲男生早前承認一項管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產罪，16歲男生則承認管有攻擊性武器等4罪。主任裁判官徐綺薇明白二人有悔意，第一時間認罪，但強調不能忽略案發環境情況。二人處於正在進行示威的商場，案發時超過200人聚集及叫口號，有人破壞閉路電視，二人裝束與示威者一致。法庭需保障公眾利益及兼顧阻嚇性，今於西九龍裁判法院判18歲男生入勞教中心，另判16歲男生入更生中心。<br />\n<br />\n辯方為18歲男生求情指，被告患專注力不足及對立反抗症，報告內容雖認為勞教比更生中心更適合，但辯方擔心高未能承受勞教中心體力勞動，故希望法庭判更生中心。惟徐官認為他經醫生評估後被認為適合勞教中心，證明其心理質素可接受相關訓練；另外涉案的有機溶劑可對自己及他人構成威脅，乃判被告入勞教中心，接受嚴格紀律訓練。<br />\n<br />\n辯方為16歲男生求情指，被告深切反省及沒有意圖傷人。徐官表示需同時考慮更生及懲處，判刑需具阻嚇性，需判處拘禁式刑罰，故判他入更生中心。<br />\n<br />\n18歲男生承認一項管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產罪指，他於去年5月10日在旺角新世紀廣場的公眾地方保管或控制一罐噴漆及一個樽內有易燃有機溶劑。16歲男生則被指管有噴漆、無線電通訊機、雷射筆及索帶，被控管有攻擊性武器、管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產、沒有按照牌照規定而管有無線電器具及管有適合作非法用途的工具並意圖作非法用途使用4罪。"},{"pid":"c7a33949256dd778f5a85109c0ed814ea138e6c0","tid":2497014,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ae8aa574400d6469b5aecd564ae1afd9183159","tid":2497014,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5da73d023bafa9b2f567a835cb3ec34a4df8ac4","tid":2497014,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c4a9c6dbc5762112236928c231bc690e4c47e0","tid":2497014,"uid":57513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:28:26.000Z","msg":"又少兩個高達創建者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b50d07e9527573974208b68264fb138137b3d7","tid":2497014,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:30:54.000Z","msg":"都真係好撚阻嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7bd5718040b652c44be96e2c6fb0b72a14630e","tid":2497014,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52082bdaba1e99c762c8155c08ea2c1db3052d3e","tid":2497014,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:03:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5912f27d4ecd877bf3406795838b241173b433","tid":2497014,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:04:18.000Z","msg":"辯方指，次被告已還押三星期，現時就讀中四，仍然在學，被告很希望可以繼續學業，未來向工程方向發展，希望法庭可以用不影響他學業的方式判刑，建議考慮社會服務令。鑑於判入中心的刑期不能扣減，辯方指若不判服務令，則可考慮短期監禁，讓被告早日回校讀書。但徐官明言，<span class=\"red\">除非沒有其他更適合的選擇，法庭才會考慮判監。</span><a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210420/PHJX6CXFBNEWTI7EBWOZS75UWY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210420%2FPHJX6CXFBNEWTI7EBWOZS75UWY%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJxmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=6cbd0e3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210420%2FPHJX6CXFBNEWTI7EBWOZS75UWY%2F&h=98094a2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210420/PHJX6CXFBNEWTI7EBWOZS75UWY/</a>"},{"pid":"856dc794197d0cc602ed02446a59df0041de1c67","tid":2497014,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:35:48.000Z","msg":"首被告患有專注力缺乏症及對立反抗症 仍被判入勞教中心<br />\n<br />\n至於同樣患有專注力缺乏症及過度活躍症的 15 歲男學生，辯方指他原本與家人關係疏離，但接受輔導後有所改善。雖然他成績一般，但品行良好。他在還押 3 星期間已有深切反省，明白到守法的重要性，承諾日後會以合法方式表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n辯方望法庭考慮他有悔意，可以判處社會服務令，相信不會對其學業造成很大影響。但假如法庭認為不適合，建議以短期監禁處理，而非判入勞教或更生中心。惟裁判官表示，根據處理年輕犯人的相關指引，監禁是別無他選的情況下才會判處，且報告顯示男學生同樣適合被判入勞教及更生中心。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/5-10-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E8%AA%8D%E6%94%9C%E9%90%B3%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86%E5%8F%8A%E6%98%93%E7%87%83%E6%B6%B2-%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%88%A4%E5%85%A5%E5%8B%9E%E6%95%99-%E6%9B%B4%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F5-10-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%2594%259C%25E9%2590%25B3%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%2598%2593%25E7%2587%2583%25E6%25B6%25B2-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%258B%259E%25E6%2595%2599-%25E6%259B%25B4%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJxmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=286b31e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F5-10-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%2594%259C%25E9%2590%25B3%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%2598%2593%25E7%2587%2583%25E6%25B6%25B2-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%258B%259E%25E6%2595%2599-%25E6%259B%25B4%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%2F&h=69d646c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/5-10-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E8%AA%8D%E6%94%9C%E9%90%B3%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86%E5%8F%8A%E6%98%93%E7%87%83%E6%B6%B2-%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%88%A4%E5%85%A5%E5%8B%9E%E6%95%99-%E6%9B%B4%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/</a>"},{"pid":"da08d97daace383d0e0395cb713d42569b9a52fe","tid":2497014,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}